<p>Just made these cookies!! SO YUMMY! I hand mixed them and took them out in 10 minutes. I made two batches, one on a greased pan (which came out slightly crunchy on the bottom) and one on a non-greased pan (which is still in the oven <img src='http://erincooks.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' />  ) This is way better than the premade stuff I usually get!</p>
